de_documents

Map by HR (Hellraz0r)


The Terrorists's have blown a hole and infiltrated the 'warehouse' looking for government documents. Just before the workers were shot, they hit the alarm and the Counter Terrorists's were contacted by locals hearing noises coming from the warehouse. The Counter Terrorists's drive in by APC's and proceed by foot.

Note: This was originally dtn_bloodstrike(you'll notice the the warehouse)

ANY BUGS/SUGGESTIONS, PLEASE EMAIL ME AT: hellraz0r1337@gmail.com
